xEvil is an excellent, addictive side scrolling game. Originally written for linux it has been ported to Windows. Sadly, it has not been ported to the [[MacOS]].

Hopefully it can be cloned for the [[NewtonOS]]. More info can be found [here ](http://www.xevil.com).

